title: Kim Kardashian Goes on Date Night With Hubby Kanye West Hours Before Having Stretch Marks Removed
text: Kim Kardashian Goes on Date Night With Hubby Kanye West Hours Before Having Stretch Marks Removed by Emily Krauser 6:10 PM PST, February 19, 2017 Photo: Splash News Even Kimye need a night out minus the kids! Kanye West and Kim Kardashian West stepped out for dinner in Woodland Hills, California, on Saturday night, just a few days after spending time in New York City, where the rapper-turned-designer was showing his Yeezy Season 5 collection during New York Fashion Week . WATCH: Kim Kardashian Celebrates Paris Hilton's Birthday With Platinum Blonde Hair Kanye, 39, topped a white graphic tee and navy blue track pants with a denim jacket covered in floral embroidery, while Kim, 36, wore one of her favorite brown fur coats over a sheer black tee, matching Yeezy pants and lace-up booties. Photo: Splash News Just hours later, Kim was at the doctor's office for a little cosmetic upgrade -- removing her stretch marks. She took to Snapchat to tell her followers all about the procedure, using the voice-altering rabbit filter for good measure. "So I just left Dr. Ourian's office and we worked on stretch marks today, and I feel so excited that I finally did it," the mom of two said on Sunday. "I've been so scared to do it thinking it'd hurt so badly, and it didn't hurt that badly. So I'm so grateful, and I'm so excited. I love you, Dr. Ourian." A post shared by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 19, 2017 at 10:05am PST WATCH: Kim Kardashian Unveils More Sexy Bikini Pics from Her Trip to Costa Rica Once home, Kim continued to play around on Snapchat with her 3-year-old daughter, North West, who was also enthralled with the app's bunny ears. "You're so cute," the Keeping Up with the Kardashians star told Norie as the toddler made animal noises into the camera. The mother-daughter duo also tested out the infinity pool filter and put on their beloved digital flower crowns. A post shared by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 19, 2017 at 10:43am PST A post shared by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 19, 2017 at 10:46am PST A post shared by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 19, 2017 at 10:54am PST February has been nothing but fashion and love for Kim and Kanye.
